{"tid":1965631,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"十大最低觀看次數港台節目，你有冇睇過？","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T04:26:09.000Z","uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35183407494e683da6f1220b24ebb1a3dcbd7812","tid":1965631,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"咁多機械人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/fc/fc/w_q/cedb-cci-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Ffc%2Fw_q%2Fcedb-cci-c.pdf&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=3aff3573\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/fc/fc/w_q/cedb-cci-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年7月1日至2020年3月10日期間，10個最低觀看次數電視節目的累計數字，表列如下：<br />\n節目 觀看次數<br />\n1. 亞太廣播聯盟機械人大賽2017－飛碟爭霸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1 741<br />\n2. West Kowloon Cultural Districtin the Making 2019<br />\n1 911<br />\n3. 花豚錦簇喜迎春 <br />\n2 407<br />\n4. 西九進行式2019 <br />\n2 638<br />\n5. 亞太廣播聯盟機械人大賽2019<br />\n2 662<br />\n6. 全港大專生機械人大賽2017－飛碟爭霸<br />\n4 368<br />\n7. 全港大專生機械人大賽2019 <br />\n4 509<br />\n8. 有問有答《基本法》問答比賽決賽2019<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4 560<br />\n9. 第41屆十大中文金曲 「用心聽」音樂會前奏<br />\n5 903<br />\n10. 中國故事III (尼泊爾語字幕) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6 000"},{"pid":"d984d15030b5e558ba51041114c145ba2c4cb3bc","tid":1965631,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"2016年7月1日至2020年3月10日期間，10個最高觀看次數電視節目的累計數字，表列如下：<br />\n節目 觀看次數<br />\n1. 鏗鏘集 4 114萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 頭條新聞 1 934萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 視點31 1 420萬<br />\n4. 城市論壇 1 233萬<br />\n5. 早辰・早晨 725萬<br />\n<del>6. 警訊 636萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del><br />\n7. 議事論事 602萬<br />\n8. 沒有牆的世界6 278萬<br />\n9. 火速救兵IV 273萬<br />\n10. 香港故事－璀璨之後 271萬"},{"pid":"a74688ca13507bf875d2a1a1917e74d07cf72c62","tid":1965631,"uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"問題：<br />\n請告知本會，在現時市民對警隊信任度極低下，為何《警訊》仍能佔據香<br />\n港電台黃金時段而不被其他資訊性節目取代；以及為何只有警隊擁有每 周<br />\n能在電視上播放的節目，而其他紀律部隊，包括但不限於消防、懲教、海<br />\n關、入境處卻沒有擁有屬於自己的節目？<br />\n提問人：楊岳橋議員 (立法會內部參考編號： 221)<br />\n<br />\n答覆：<br />\n作為香港的公共廣播機構，香港電台多年來與不同政府部門合作，製作不<br />\n同類型的節目，讓市民認識政府不同部門 的服務及為市民提供各種資訊。<br />\n《警訊》為觀眾提供防止罪案資訊及案件消息呼籲，符 合公眾利益。"},{"pid":"25edf17930ad27460388c45df57afd496781977e","tid":1965631,"uid":306598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"31 看世界咁好睇都入唔到十大最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c537c8898606e55eba17a5f17d82e0f48e2a99c3","tid":1965631,"uid":33734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"25edf17930ad27460388c45df57afd496781977e","tid":1965631,"uid":306598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"31 看世界咁好睇都入唔到十大最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"五夜講場咁高汁都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85ddbd8d6f388d98c1f82a3e7e86ca98f01a559","tid":1965631,"uid":148355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"香港歷史系列同功夫傳奇都好高質"},{"pid":"38c0d4a9fed508cbf30f9f6115e93d119226795a","tid":1965631,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c537c8898606e55eba17a5f17d82e0f48e2a99c3","tid":1965631,"uid":33734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"25edf17930ad27460388c45df57afd496781977e","tid":1965631,"uid":306598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"31 看世界咁好睇都入唔到十大最高<img sr